  "prompt": "I am going to organising an party, for that I need to clean my home on or before 31/12/2017. So suggest me cleaning service company in Perth?",
  "response": "Sure, finding a reliable cleaning service is important for preparing your home for a party. Here are some reputable cleaning services in Perth that you can consider:\n\n1. **MaidPerfect** - Known for their thorough cleaning services and professional staff, MaidPerfect offers a range of cleaning packages tailored to different needs.\n\n2. **Home Cleaning Perth** - Offers comprehensive cleaning services including deep cleaning, regular housekeeping, and end-of-lease cleaning. They are known for their attention to detail and customer satisfaction.\n\n3. **Perth Home Cleaners** - Specializes in residential cleaning with flexible scheduling and competitive pricing. They have a good reputation for quality service and reliability.\n\n4. **Housekeeping WA** - Provides a wide range of domestic cleaning services, including one-time deep cleans and ongoing maintenance. They are known for their friendly staff and efficient service.\n\n5. **Cleaning Force** - Offers professional cleaning services with a focus on eco-friendly products and methods. They are well-regarded for their thoroughness and reliability.\n\nMake sure to contact them in advance to check their availability and book a slot before your party date.",
